{"tid":997322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"海關扣貨。。想知我係未比人呃","createTime":"2019-01-27T05:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T12:41:47.000Z","uid":207094,"like":7,"dislike":422,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"4198434d3a5ee7c2f37dd1759fd7fd95b0fba109","tid":997322,"uid":207094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:35:59.000Z","msg":"我向網上識左個住美國嘅朋友。。<br />\n傾傾下某一日佢話買左份禮物比我。。<br />\n但由於過重/清關 要比約1500 USD-2000 USD。<br />\n他說已將等值嘅現金放在包裏裡。<br />\n我唔記得左放錢份包裹係犯法<br />\n所以都無提佢<br />\n<br />\n到左過左2日。。有間叫ON-TIME DELIVERY SERVICES an affiliate of DHL嘅通知我 件貨尼左香港 叫我先比關稅及清關費 $13000 HKD...我比左<br />\n<br />\n之後佢地話因為件貨向交貨前最後掃描掃到有錢。。比海關扣起要求保釋金$93000。。<br />\n<br />\n我同我美國個朋友講返。。佢話佢得$30000 HKD向美國。。佢都唔知點做好<br />\n<br />\n我想知呢個情況係咪似騙案多?<br />\n海關扣貨個程序係點? 扣左係咪海關會打電話通知收貨人 即係我?<br />\n美國個朋友佢話2星期後先返到香港。。係咪應該等佢返尼香港先處理?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59a97144cf35001ec4766c2c45e55fdb12312ad","tid":997322,"uid":199774,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"派膠？"},{"pid":"00d65e5cc452b275421771ac0a3a2380952618cf","tid":997322,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01